room_title: Escape room "8-Bit Escape" by Escape Room Herndon in Washington, D.C.
room_description: Your friends have come over to play your newest video game but once you get to the basement you see your mom has locked up all your gaming gear until you finish your homework. You and your friends have 60 minutes to find all your gear and put it back together before your mom kicks them out and they all go over to Wade's house.
